title: Amy Feels Like A Terrible Parent + Bobby Calls Out The Haters
itunes:title: Amy Feels Like A Terrible Parent + Bobby Calls Out The Haters
description:
Amy shares what she did that makes her feel like a terrible parent. Bobby calls out some online haters for being rude about an artist that was on the show. Lunchbox tries to get free stuff for Father's Day. Also, Blanco Brown stops by the studio.
